name: Cupid Fore
text: If all monsters you control are monsters with 600 DEF (min. 1): You can Special Summon this card from your hand. (Quick Effect): You can discard 1 card, then target 1 LIGHT Fairy monster you control and 1 face-up monster on the field; the Level of that monster you control becomes the Level of the other monster until the end of this turn. You can only use each effect of "Cupid Fore" once per turn.
